Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz has activated the second barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Orichalcos Deuteros!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With it, he regains Life Points on every one of his turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we're not able to Direct Attack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And... the Monsters he's Summoned onto the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Mirror Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their true identities are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The souls that were stolen - Partner, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} and others as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's really dirty, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Captive Mirror Knights"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz, that's a really cheap trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All souls that have been taken are under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh! Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of your comrades have taken residence within the Mirror Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will heed to my will as my loyal pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really low, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am simply giving you a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to sacrifice your souls as they are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you would be of the lowest ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz...! You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh. Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the both of you to struggle and suffer {\i1}much{\i0} more than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have, the darkness in your hearts will have grown tremendously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you will have become fitting offerings for my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my Mirror Knight Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed with an attack on the Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho? You still possess the will to oppose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see how far the bonds you all place your faith in ever so will get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and finish my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I've destroyed Mirror Knight Calling, they can no longer regenerate with that Immortality Ability they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! I activate Pot of Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I add two cards from my deck to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate Cost Down from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding a card from my hand, this card reduces a Monster's Level by two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I Summon Different Dimension Dragon - Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight Zone Dragon cannot be destroyed in battle by a Monster with 1900 or less Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaiser Glider is a Monster that can't be destroyed by a Monster that has the same Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I've completed my lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my Kaiser Glider to attack Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}serious{\i0}, Kaiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz, if this is some kind of trap you've set up, it's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no difference to me that they are acting as your warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All standing in my way, {\i1}whoever{\i0} they may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will just mercilessly destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you {\i1}understand{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this is a restraining trap he's set for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that if we lose here, all the souls that were taken will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my promise with Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I attack them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen when they disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I haven't a clue as to where {\i1}dead{\i0} souls reside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor do I have the time to ponder the mysteries of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kaiser Glider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and attack Mirror Knight Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Mirror Shield disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she takes the next attack, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After, I attack with Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...guarded Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amusing scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unconscious Jounouchi actually {\i1}guarded{\i0} Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all that means is the bonds you share within your hearts will only fortify my alignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Deadbeat...\N Always getting in the way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, Jounouchi and Mai are defenseless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pacifist! Do you intend to stay back and wait for your loss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every one of them here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...are irreplaceable friends to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will end my turn without doing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the other Yugi could attack any of them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfair! This Dartz bastard's playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, as a result of Orichalcos Deuteros' effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Life increases by 2500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one were to say your destiny can be decided at will, allow me to decide it {\i1}for{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuous Magic! Double Centaur Archer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Centaur Archer will fire its arrow towards one of our teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster it hits is removed from the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Attack Power of that Monster shall be casted upon the player as damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The targets will be Kaiser Glider and Mirror Knight Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Jounouchi will disappear if he gets hit with that arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could also hit my brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny beckons you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny appears to have chosen {\i1}you{\i0}, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the turn I activate Double Centaur Archer's abilities, I am unable to attack with a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I will be ending my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wretched dolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure, I'll dispose of that pitiable wreck once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Twilight Zone Dragon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadbeat! If you have even a shred of Duelist's pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,act like a man and be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, Yugi guarded Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see how magnificent your bond is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defend one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Protect{\i0} one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul prisoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't destroy that Continuous Magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he'll once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick-Play Magic! Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this card to destroy Double Centaur Archer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you destroy Double Centaur Archer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, your Life is nothing more than a light flickering in the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise, Orichalcos Diabolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to the effects of Orichalcos Deuteros,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Life rises to 15500!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15500...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that Monster attacks my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a shame, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that this is as far as you proceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But among your sacrifice, a new world lies in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Diablos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Guidance Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card allows me to switch the attack target to another Defense Mode Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increase their Defense Power by 600 points in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Shield Gardna!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes Big Shield Gardna's Defense Power greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all the damage I receive is absorbed by Orichalcos Kyutora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he receives an attack, Big Shield Gardna switches into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of the effect of Attack Guidance Barrier, your turn is forced to a close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've spared your life but a moment longer, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've given you temporary aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I only have 600 Life Points left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I can't Summon any of the Monsters in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Twilight Zone Dragon into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards on the field and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, Summon a Monster and {\i1}attack{\i0} them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget... about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have... a much more important mission ahead of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are fully prepared to be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, Partner... In order to rescue you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's wrong with you, Nameless Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Big Shield Gardna into Defense Mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Placing a reverse card face-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finish off my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh. Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you are nothing more than beings struggling against destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will come to know your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that everyone has darkness within their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can still be shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still possibility among the human beings on this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael... I certainly never expected to hear those words uttered from {\i1}your{\i0} mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dartz... The fact is, I have been saved from the darkness in my heart by the Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the souls of Varon and Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return them to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael... Do you {\i1}truly{\i0} believe you have been saved from the darkness residing within your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you referring to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred... Sadness... Despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} possible to remove these things from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is true, then why...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Because these things alone do not make up the "truth" behind humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The... truth behind humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am talking about those who have attempted to extinguish the darkness in their hearts long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaze your eyes towards the inhabitants of these slates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many of them were wise beyond humanity and learned how to free themselves of the darkness in their hearts and their troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing so, they found peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even {\i1}they{\i0} could not {\i1}completely{\i0} eliminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because the human spirit holds onto the smallest of fragments of discontent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the darkness in their hearts continued to come closer to them once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...their hearts became weak and fickle as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That is wrong, Lord Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings they hold deep within themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have taught me the importance of the strength they possess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from now on, my soul will no longer be swallowed by the darkness in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} gives some meaning to what Yugi's been risking his life for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dartz...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to {\i1}enlighten{\i0} you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the true identity of the darkness of the heart and where it generates from from within humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All{\i0} of you should have it {\i1}somewhere{\i0} within your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For human beings are insecure creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're saying that's {\i1}wrong{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with people inferring such ambiguous terms such as "possibility" the way they see fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is no {\i1}wonder{\i0} they are insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how about facing {\i1}reality{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with wealth, those who neglect, those with anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with talent, those with reason, those who are blessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are hated simply because they were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is destined to be plagued by imperfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what drives the darkness of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}no one{\i0} is able to escape from that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the {\i1}truth{\i0} of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I am trying to rebuild this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the goal of creating perfect human beings capable of warding off the darkness of their hearts in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Varon and Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are also tenacious warriors born with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the purpose of indulging in the darkness of your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For I required beings who questioned their fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny created these powerful beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his beloved younger brother at the hands of weaponry created by Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he welcomed the darkness in his heart with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true, Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Amelda went after my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, on that very same battlefield he lost his brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Gozaburo Kaiba {\i1}truly{\i0} the one responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who burned down Varon's orphanage until it was nothing more than a pile of cinders...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it that the one ship you happened to be riding conveniently sunk to the bottom of the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why was it that you alone managed to survive such a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}couldn't{\i0} have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brod'er!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sonia!! Julien!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no {\i1}way{\i0} that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your destinies were decided from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply gave them a slight... shove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For I {\i1}needed{\i0} you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inevitable resurrection of the Legendary Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Chosen Duelists whom they fell under the control of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed beings who could control the darkness within their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Formidable pawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! How could you do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother and my little sister...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are of little importance in the face of Doma's mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! You {\i1}bastard{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rafael's barrier should have already disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop right now, Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once activated, the Barrier of Orichalcos will {\i1}never{\i0} completely vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is irrefutable proof that the darkness of your heart never once left you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become food for the rebirth of my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael... You have shown us the inevitable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That people will never completely rid themselves of the darkness infesting their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz...! You {\i1}monster{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our interference has left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh! Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will reveal the true power of the Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I offer you onto my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true power...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Tritos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz has activated the third barrier of the Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Tritos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:22:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the three boundaries in play, the Barrier of Orichalcos has been completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only can we not attack with our comrade's Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our Direct Attacks have been sealed away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Yugi and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} get out of this desperate situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Third Barrier of Orichalcos"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:23:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
